42
00:03:28,734 --> 00:03:30,134
Tunggu, Conan!

43
00:03:30,134 --> 00:03:31,634
Conan!

44
00:03:31,634 --> 00:03:33,434
Petugas Chiba, maukah kamu mengambil mobilnya.

45
00:03:33,434 --> 00:03:34,434
Ya.

46
00:03:34,434 --> 00:03:36,934
"Hiramune."

47
00:03:40,334 --> 00:03:41,734
Tidak ada jawaban.

48
00:03:48,734 --> 00:03:49,834
Itu buka.

49
00:03:55,034 --> 00:03:56,534
Tuan Hiramune.

50
00:03:56,534 --> 00:03:57,734
Apa kau di sana?

51
