146
00:08:22,734 --> 00:08:25,534
Sato dan Chiba, tanyakan orang-orang di sekitar sini.

147
00:08:25,534 --> 00:08:26,534
-Siap, pak. -Siap, pak.

148
00:08:26,534 --> 00:08:28,734
